                  <p class="text-sky-600 font-medium">Interactive Space Dashboard</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <p class="text-ink-700 mb-6">
                A visually immersive web dashboard inspired by real NASA missions, designed to engage users with satellite tracking, mission metadata, and weather visualizations on Mars.
              </p>
              
