          "Every project is an opportunity to solve a problem, learn something new, and create something that makes a difference — no matter how small."
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-lavender-400 to-lavender-600 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
